&lt;/script&gt;
{% endif %}

Modify context_processors.py:

def google_analytics(request):
    from django.conf import settings
    return {"GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID": getattr(settings, "GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID", "")}

Add context processor in settings.py:

