CSS Grid and Flexbox

CSS Grid: Best for two-dimensional layouts, allowing for both rows and columns.
Flexbox: Best for one-dimensional layouts, controlling the layout of items along a single axis. &gt; Example (CSS Grid)

.grid-container {
